&lt;h2&gt;Frequently Asked Questions&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;circle-point&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&#34;col-sm-12 col-xs-12 col-md-12 col-lg-12 lt&#34;&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;create-tools-inn accordion&#34; itemscope=&#34;&#34; itemtype=&#34;http://schema.org/FAQPage&#34;&gt;
&lt;div itemscope itemprop=&#34;mainEntity&#34; itemtype=&#34;http://schema.org/Question&#34;&gt;
&lt;div id=&#34;bt1&#34; class=&#34;tog accordion-head first open&#34;&gt;&lt;span itemprop=&#34;name&#34;&gt;How to Create Quizzes&lt;/span&gt; &lt;i class=&#34;arrow2 down&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;toggle-div accordion-body&#34; id=&#34;cont1&#34; itemscope itemprop=&#34;acceptedAnswer&#34; itemtype=&#34;http://schema.org/Answer&#34; style=&#34;display:block;overflow:hidden&#34;&gt;
&lt;p itemprop=&#34;text&#34;&gt;Creating an online quiz is as easy as drag and drop of questions from our ready-to-use question library. Choose a scored quiz or personality quiz template, or create one from scratch, pull in questions from our library, add media to your quiz and there you go! Watch this short video to learn &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.youtube.com/embed/NxIWsERigFs?autoplay=1&amp;rel=0&#34; title=&#34;How to Create a Scored Quiz&#34; class=&#34;popup-youtube&#34;&gt;How to Create Quizzes Easily&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

function getCookieutm(cname) {
	var name = cname + &#34;=&#34;;
	var decodedCookie = decodeURIComponent(document.cookie);
	var ca = decodedCookie.split(&#39;;&#39;);
	for (var i = 0; i &lt; ca.length; i++) {
		var c = ca[i];
		while (c.charAt(0) == &#39; &#39;) {
			c = c.substring(1);
		}
		if (c.indexOf(name) == 0) {
			return c.substring(name.length, c.length);
		}
	}
	return &#34;&#34;;
}

var keyCodeMap = {
        48:&#34;0&#34;, 49:&#34;1&#34;, 50:&#34;2&#34;, 51:&#34;3&#34;, 52:&#34;4&#34;, 53:&#34;5&#34;, 54:&#34;6&#34;, 55:&#34;7&#34;, 56:&#34;8&#34;, 57:&#34;9&#34;, 59:&#34;;&#34;,
        65:&#34;a&#34;, 66:&#34;b&#34;, 67:&#34;c&#34;, 68:&#34;d&#34;, 69:&#34;e&#34;, 70:&#34;f&#34;, 71:&#34;g&#34;, 72:&#34;h&#34;, 73:&#34;i&#34;, 74:&#34;j&#34;, 75:&#34;k&#34;, 76:&#34;l&#34;,
        77:&#34;m&#34;, 78:&#34;n&#34;, 79:&#34;o&#34;, 80:&#34;p&#34;, 81:&#34;q&#34;, 82:&#34;r&#34;, 83:&#34;s&#34;, 84:&#34;t&#34;, 85:&#34;u&#34;, 86:&#34;v&#34;, 87:&#34;w&#34;, 88:&#34;x&#34;, 89:&#34;y&#34;, 90:&#34;z&#34;,
        96:&#34;0&#34;, 97:&#34;1&#34;, 98:&#34;2&#34;, 99:&#34;3&#34;, 100:&#34;4&#34;, 101:&#34;5&#34;, 102:&#34;6&#34;, 103:&#34;7&#34;, 104:&#34;8&#34;, 105:&#34;9&#34;
}

$.fn.setup_navigation = function(settings) {

	settings = jQuery.extend({
		menuHoverClass: &#39;show-menu&#39;,
	}, settings);
	
	// Add ARIA role to menubar and menu items
	$(this).attr(&#39;role&#39;, &#39;menubar&#39;).find(&#39;li&#39;).attr(&#39;role&#39;, &#39;menuitem&#39;);
	
	var top_level_links = $(this).find(&#39;&gt; li &gt; a&#39;);

	// Added by Terrill: (removed temporarily: doesn&#39;t fix the JAWS problem after all)
	// Add tabindex=&#34;0&#34; to all top-level links 
	// Without at least one of these, JAWS doesn&#39;t read widget as a menu, despite all the other ARIA
	//$(top_level_links).attr(&#39;tabindex&#39;,&#39;0&#39;);
	
	// Set tabIndex to -1 so that top_level_links can&#39;t receive focus until menu is open
	$(top_level_links).next(&#39;ul&#39;)
		.attr(&#39;data-test&#39;,&#39;true&#39;)
		.attr({ &#39;aria-hidden&#39;: &#39;true&#39;, &#39;role&#39;: &#39;menu&#39; })
		.find(&#39;a&#39;)
			.attr(&#39;tabIndex&#39;,-1);
	
	// Adding aria-haspopup for appropriate items
	$(top_level_links).each(function(){
		if($(this).next(&#39;ul&#39;).length &gt; 0)
			$(this).parent(&#39;li&#39;).attr(&#39;aria-haspopup&#39;, &#39;true&#39;);
	});
	
//	$(top_level_links).hover(function(){
//		$(this).closest(&#39;ul&#39;) 
//			.attr(&#39;aria-hidden&#39;, &#39;false&#39;)
//			.find(&#39;.&#39;+settings.menuHoverClass)
//				.attr(&#39;aria-hidden&#39;, &#39;true&#39;)
//				.removeClass(settings.menuHoverClass)
//				.find(&#39;a&#39;)
//					.attr(&#39;tabIndex&#39;,-1);
//		$(this).next(&#39;ul&#39;)
//			.attr(&#39;aria-hidden&#39;, &#39;false&#39;)
//			.addClass(settings.menuHoverClass)
//			.find(&#39;a&#39;).attr(&#39;tabIndex&#39;,0);
//	});
	$(top_level_links).focus(function(){
		$(this).closest(&#39;ul&#39;)
			// Removed by Terrill 
			// The following was adding aria-hidden=&#34;false&#34; to root ul since menu is never hidden
			// and seemed to be causing flakiness in JAWS (needs more testing) 
			// .attr(&#39;aria-hidden&#39;, &#39;false&#39;) 
			.find(&#39;.&#39;+settings.menuHoverClass)
				.attr(&#39;aria-hidden&#39;, &#39;true&#39;)
				.removeClass(settings.menuHoverClass)
				.find(&#39;a&#39;)
					.attr(&#39;tabIndex&#39;,-1);
		$(this).next(&#39;ul&#39;)
			.attr(&#39;aria-hidden&#39;, &#39;false&#39;)
			.addClass(settings.menuHoverClass)
			.find(&#39;a&#39;).attr(&#39;tabIndex&#39;,0);
	});
	
	// Bind arrow keys for navigation
	$(top_level_links).keydown(function(e){
		if(e.keyCode == 37) {
			e.preventDefault();
			// This is the first item
			if($(this).parent(&#39;li&#39;).prev(&#39;li&#39;).length == 0) {
				$(this).parents(&#39;ul&#39;).find(&#39;&gt; li&#39;).last().find(&#39;a&#39;).first().focus();
			} else {
				$(this).parent(&#39;li&#39;).prev(&#39;li&#39;).find(&#39;a&#39;).first().focus();
			}
		} else if(e.keyCode == 38) {
			e.preventDefault();
			if($(this).parent(&#39;li&#39;).find(&#39;ul&#39;).length &gt; 0) {
				$(this).parent(&#39;li&#39;).find(&#39;ul&#39;)
					.attr(&#39;aria-hidden&#39;, &#39;false&#39;)
					.addClass(settings.menuHoverClass)
					.find(&#39;a&#39;).attr(&#39;tabIndex&#39;,0)
						.last().focus();
			}
		} else if(e.keyCode == 39) {
			e.preventDefault();
			// This is the last item
			if($(this).parent(&#39;li&#39;).next(&#39;li&#39;).length == 0) {
				$(this).parents(&#39;ul&#39;).find(&#39;&gt; li&#39;).first().find(&#39;a&#39;).first().focus();
			} else {
				$(this).parent(&#39;li&#39;).next(&#39;li&#39;).find(&#39;a&#39;).first().focus();
			}
		} else if(e.keyCode == 40) {
			e.preventDefault();
			if($(this).parent(&#39;li&#39;).find(&#39;ul&#39;).length &gt; 0) {
				$(this).parent(&#39;li&#39;).find(&#39;ul&#39;)
					.attr(&#39;aria-hidden&#39;, &#39;false&#39;)
					.addClass(settings.menuHoverClass)
					.find(&#39;a&#39;).attr(&#39;tabIndex&#39;,0)
						.first().focus();
			}
		} else if(e.keyCode == 13 || e.keyCode == 32) {
			// If submenu is hidden, open it
			e.preventDefault();
			$(this).parent(&#39;li&#39;).find(&#39;ul[aria-hidden=true]&#39;)
					.attr(&#39;aria-hidden&#39;, &#39;false&#39;)
					.addClass(settings.menuHoverClass)
					.find(&#39;a&#39;).attr(&#39;tabIndex&#39;,0)
						.first().focus();
		} else if(e.keyCode == 27) {
			e.preventDefault();
			$(&#39;.&#39;+settings.menuHoverClass)
				.attr(&#39;aria-hidden&#39;, &#39;true&#39;)
				.removeClass(settings.menuHoverClass)
				.find(&#39;a&#39;)
					.attr(&#39;tabIndex&#39;,-1);
		} else {
			$(this).parent(&#39;li&#39;).find(&#39;ul[aria-hidden=false] a&#39;).each(function(){
				if($(this).text().substring(0,1).toLowerCase() == keyCodeMap[e.keyCode]) {
					$(this).focus();
					return false;
				}
			});
		}
	});
	
	
	var links = $(top_level_links).parent(&#39;li&#39;).find(&#39;ul&#39;).find(&#39;a&#39;);
	$(links).keydown(function(e){
		if(e.keyCode == 38) {
			e.preventDefault();
			// This is the first item
			if($(this).parent(&#39;li&#39;).prev(&#39;li&#39;).length == 0) {
				$(this).parents(&#39;ul&#39;).parents(&#39;li&#39;).find(&#39;a&#39;).first().focus();
			} else {
				$(this).parent(&#39;li&#39;).prev(&#39;li&#39;).find(&#39;a&#39;).first().focus();
			}
		} else if(e.keyCode == 40) {
			e.preventDefault();
			if($(this).parent(&#39;li&#39;).next(&#39;li&#39;).length == 0) {
				$(this).parents(&#39;ul&#39;).parents(&#39;li&#39;).find(&#39;a&#39;).first().focus();
			} else {
				$(this).parent(&#39;li&#39;).next(&#39;li&#39;).find(&#39;a&#39;).first().focus();
			}
		} else if(e.keyCode == 27 || e.keyCode == 37) {
			e.preventDefault();
			$(this)
				.parents(&#39;ul&#39;).first()
					.prev(&#39;a&#39;).focus()
					.parents(&#39;ul&#39;).first().find(&#39;.&#39;+settings.menuHoverClass)
						.attr(&#39;aria-hidden&#39;, &#39;true&#39;)
						.removeClass(settings.menuHoverClass)
						.find(&#39;a&#39;)
							.attr(&#39;tabIndex&#39;,-1);
		} else if(e.keyCode == 32) {
			e.preventDefault();
			window.location = $(this).attr(&#39;href&#39;);
		} else {
			var found = false;
			$(this).parent(&#39;li&#39;).nextAll(&#39;li&#39;).find(&#39;a&#39;).each(function(){
				if($(this).text().substring(0,1).toLowerCase() == keyCodeMap[e.keyCode]) {
					$(this).focus();
					found = true;
					return false;
				}
			});
			
			if(!found) {
				$(this).parent(&#39;li&#39;).prevAll(&#39;li&#39;).find(&#39;a&#39;).each(function(){
					if($(this).text().substring(0,1).toLowerCase() == keyCodeMap[e.keyCode]) {
						$(this).focus();
						return false;
					}
				});
			}
		}
	});

		
	// Hide menu if click or focus occurs outside of navigation
	$(this).find(&#39;a&#39;).last().keydown(function(e){ 
		if(e.keyCode == 9) {
			// If the user tabs out of the navigation hide all menus
			$(&#39;.&#39;+settings.menuHoverClass)
				.attr(&#39;aria-hidden&#39;, &#39;true&#39;)
				.removeClass(settings.menuHoverClass)
				.find(&#39;a&#39;)
					.attr(&#39;tabIndex&#39;,-1);
		}
	});
	$(document).click(function(){ $(&#39;.&#39;+settings.menuHoverClass).attr(&#39;aria-hidden&#39;, &#39;true&#39;).removeClass(settings.menuHoverClass).find(&#39;a&#39;).attr(&#39;tabIndex&#39;,-1); });
	
	$(this).click(function(e){
		e.stopPropagation();
	});
}
